---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 46
By: Sri Ramana Maharshi
Tags:
  - Creation=Man’s Primordial Birthright
  - Union-Identity=Realization And Identity=Realization
---
The search ‘Who am I?’ ... ends in the annihilation of the illusory 'I'
and the Self which remains over will be as clear as a gooseberry in the
palm of one’s hand ... You are sure to realize the Self for it is your
natural state.
